package LearningStatic;

public class StaticDemo {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		
		Abc.show();
		
	}
	static class Abc
	{
		
		public static  void show() 
		{
		System.out.println("hi");}
	}
}
When a method is declared as static then there is no need to create objects for that method we can
directly call the method using class name.
